body:
I've also come upon [this issue on SO](http://stackoverflow.com/questions/41808353/tensorflow-slim-module-object-has-no-attribute-sum-of-squares) while searching for fix for vgg.

I believe `sum_of_squares_loss = slim.losses.sum_of_squares(depth_predictions, depth_labels)
` is still in README despite being deprecated, but I haven't checked it myself.

I hope this helps.
